                      </TableHead>
                      <TableHead className="font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px]">
                        Type
                      </TableHead>
                      <TableHead className="font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px]">
                        Dimensions/Size
                      </TableHead>
                      <TableHead className="font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px]">
